Home  News  Mark Andrekovich: Maximus Achieves Oracle PartnerNetwork Gold Level Status 

















Mark Andrekovich: Maximus Achieves Oracle PartnerNetwork Gold Level Status
Posted By: Jay Clemenson: December 23, 2014In: News, Products & Service Print Email
Mark Andrekovich
Maximus has attained a gold level status as member of Oracle’s PartnerNetwork for providing tax credit pre-screening services.
The company helps clients assess job candidates with Oracle-made technology in order to avail of tax incentives for hiring veterans and persons with disabilities, Maximus said Tuesday.
Mark Andrekovich, president of Maximus’ tax credit and employer services unit, said the company will extend its services to human resources professionals that seek to achieve I-9 and E-Verify compliance in accordance with federal rules.
“Maximus values our relationship with Oracle and is pleased to achieve Gold level membership in OPN,” added Andrekovich.
Maximus also works with clients to process the form I-9 with pre-populated data and encrypted electronic signatures.
