Mr. Mark S. Andrekovich is Chief Human Capital Officer at MAXIMUS, Inc.
Mr. Andrekovich was previously employed as a Managing Director-Human Resources by Banister International, Inc. and Executive Vice President-Human Resources by Interpace Diagnostics Group, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Clarion University of Pennsylvania and an MBA from Monmouth University.



